msgstr "在 AngelScript 中定义的脚本类："

#: ../../doc/invoke.rst:104
msgid "Script Function Objects"
msgstr "脚本函数对象"

#: ../../doc/invoke.rst:106
msgid ""
"``script_function`` and ``script_method`` wrap an ``asIScriptFunction*`` "
"with ownership semantics, tracking the module reference count to keep the "
"function valid even after the module is discarded. ``script_function_ref`` "
"and ``script_method_ref`` are non-owning counterparts."
msgstr ""
"``script_function`` 和 ``script_method`` 包装 ``asIScriptFunction*`` 并具有所有"
"权语义，它们跟踪模块的引用计数，以在模块被丢弃后保持函数有效。"
"``script_function_ref`` 和 ``script_method_ref`` 是对应的非拥有版本。"

#: ../../doc/invoke.rst:141
msgid ""
